<main>
	 <article>
	 <nav id="goback">
	 <p><a href="events.html">Events</a>&nbsp > Children's reading circle </p>
	 </nav>
	 <div id="titledate">
	     <h1>CHILDREN'S READING CIRCLE</h1>
	         <div id="date"><time datetime="2026-03-13T17:00">
		     <p>MARCH 13th 5 p.m </p>
		     </time>
	         </div>
			 
		     <div id="info">
	             <p>PRICE: FREE &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; LOCATION: Paperback Parlor</p>
	         </div>
	 </div>

     <div id="image">
	 <img src="bookreading.jpg">
	 </div>
	 
	 <div id="body">
	 <p>Bring your little ones (ages 4–7) for a delightful children’s
	 book reading hosted here in the Paperback Parlor! This cozy space
	 is the perfect setting for young imaginations to flourish, offering
	 a warm and welcoming environment where kids can relax, listen, and let
	 their creativity bloom. The event is designed to be engaging and gentle,
	 making it ideal for early readers and curious minds alike.</p>

     <p>This special session will be led by the lovely kindergarten teacher Maura Jones,
	 who brings stories to life with a wonderful blend of warmth, expression, and imagination.
	 Her storytelling style invites children into each tale, encouraging them to connect with 
	 characters and explore new ideas. It’s more than just a reading; it’s an interactive experience
	 that nurtures curiosity.</p>

     <p>Whether your child is already a book lover or just beginning to discover the magic of stories,
	 this event offers a wonderful opportunity to spark a lifelong love of reading. Join us for a charming
	 literary moment that is sure to leave young hearts inspired and eager for more adventures on the page.</p>
	 </div>
	 
	 </article>
	 

</main>


